postcontent: For sale is this classic version of the PTR 91, which is a clone of the HK-91. And “clone” isn’t exactly a fair description because this is a quality-made rifle by all accounts. I am selling mainly because my interests are going in a different direction, and I’d like to free up some room in my safe. I will sell this gun with the tri-rail front hand guard that came on it from the preceding owner, and a half-dozen box mags, most of which are original HK-made.
